Department of Corrections spokeswoman Michelle Lyons said Thursday that the convicted sex offender was still on the run . Comeaux was in a wheelchair Monday when he pulled a gun on two guards during a transfer from a unit in Huntsville to one in Beaumont . Both guards were released after being forced to drive to the Baytown area , where Comeaux ran way . Comeaux was serving life in prison for aggravated sexual assault out of Brazos County .
